ute any unwanted relics. And second, we argue that, in order to obtain\nthermal inflation in the closed string moduli sector, one needs to go beyond\nthe present EFT description.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Apr 2009 02:41:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Oct 2009 14:51:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-09"}
