 extracts, by contrast,\nthe opposite effect is observed, in agreement with the current understanding\nthat large cells use additional mechanisms to regulate the duration of the\nmitotic phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Apr 2009 09:32:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Apr 2009 03:58:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 21 Jan 2011 09:12:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-05-29"}
